videos.headline: Broncos air it out for a 87-yard TD
videos.description: Brett Rypien delivers a long pass to A.J. Richardson who takes it to the house for a 87-yard touchdown early in the first quarter.

videos.headline: Rypien strikes again for a Boise State TD
videos.description: Brett Rypien throws a nice 8-yard touchdown pass to Sean Modster in the end zone to extend the Broncos lead 17-0.

videos.headline: Air Force answers with short TD run
videos.description: Nate Romine's 1-yard rushing touchdown puts the Falcons on the board in the first quarter.

videos.headline: Broncos scoop and score extends lead
videos.description: Air Force Nate Romine loses the football after being sacked by Jabril Frazier. Tyler Horton picks it up and returns it 21 yards for a Boise State touchdown.

videos.headline: Air Force's Romine hooks up with Bennett for big gain
videos.description: Nate Romine delivers a 29 yard pass to Marcus Bennett for a first down.  This would result in a 45-yard field goal for the Falcons.

videos.headline: Rypien hits Evans for Boise State TD
videos.description: Brett Rypien finds Octavius Evans in the end zone for a 7 yard touchdown to extend Broncos lead 34-10,

videos.headline: Wolpin 1-yard rushing TD adds to Broncos lead
videos.description: Ryan Wolpin punches it in for a Boise State touchdown with less than two minutes remaining in the fourth quarter.
